    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/177732ab93de6a71a218f7e71a07cb50.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/8cb3002e2ab543bd987c5bd0f19b9a28.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >加入与巨怪的史诗级战斗，挑战各种类型、体型和能力的老怪，试图突破不可能。你能通关吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/eeaf846260f0bd91ffa1019d935a983e.poster.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/eeaf846260f0bd91ffa1019d935a983e.webm?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/eeaf846260f0bd91ffa1019d935a983e.mp4?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/431847be40505d7787e460c56ed27b7a.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >随着你慢慢解锁不同的记忆片段，在试图揭开这个神秘世界的真相，并找寻自我的过程中，踏上这段自我发现之旅。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/76f279310827e4aeb245c528cd60865f.poster.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/76f279310827e4aeb245c528cd60865f.webm?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/76f279310827e4aeb245c528cd60865f.mp4?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/68d0ced38309d214d7ffe5ee2ae4745e.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在独立开发者创作的以其个人亲子故事为背景的游戏中，探索一个充满秘密和古老奇迹的世界，揭开你与父亲疏远的真相。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/599b89b41d2596d9c1c4897f1d5e42a9.poster.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/599b89b41d2596d9c1c4897f1d5e42a9.webm?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/599b89b41d2596d9c1c4897f1d5e42a9.mp4?t=1770885220\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2135000/extras/9b60169bd6467ac3b83b029238f2674a.avif?t=1770885220\" width=800 height=150 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家好！我是 Jugraaj（又名 JSS Games），Norigin 背后的独立开发者。这款游戏最初完全是我在下班后，在有限的时间里独立开发的。开发了几年之后，我便全身心地投入到了该项目中。目前，我还是独立开发者，但是偶尔也会根据开发进度，与特定承包商进行临时合作。我的目标始终未变，就是要把这款梦境游戏带到现实中来。 <br>- -</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>如果你对这款游戏感兴趣，别忘了把 Norigin 加入你的愿望清单</i></p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>加入邮件列表，即可定期获取更新信息，并成为 Norigin“内部消息”社群的一员！</i></p></li></ul>",
